ears, but this is the first one that truly works for both of us. My wife's shoulder pain has completely disappeared and even my snoring has improved. We're absolutely thrilled with our purchase.</p>\n        <span class=\"skc-reviewer\">— Eric &amp; Marie</span>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"skc-review-card\">\n        <img class=\"skc-review-photo\" src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/WhatsAppImage2025-08-31at11.45.47.jpg\" alt=\"Customer review\" />\n        <div class=\"skc-review-quote\">&#8220;</div>\n        <div class=\"skc-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <h4>Goodbye Morning Headaches.</h4>\n        <p>I used to wake up every morning with tension headaches from bad pillows, but that's all in the past now! This pillow gives my neck perfect support and feels firm yet wonderfully soft. I'm finally sleeping better than I have in years.</p>\n        <span class=\"skc-reviewer\">— Anna T.</span>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ===== 7. COMPARISON TABLE ===== -->\n  <section class=\"skc-compare\">\n    <div class=\"skc-compare-inner\">\n      <div class=\"skc-compare-text\">\n        <h2>What makes our support pillow so special?</h2>\n        <p>Discover why the <strong>Movanella Comfort™ Support Pillow</strong> makes all the difference compared to regular pillows on the market.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <table class=\"skc-table\">\n          <thead>\n            <tr>\n              <th></th>\n              <th>Movanella</th>\n              <th>Other Pillows</th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td>No neck pain</td>\n              <td class=\"skc-col-ours\"><span class=\"skc-check\">✓</span></td>\n              <td><span class=\"skc-cross\">✗</span></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>For all sleep positions</td>\n              <td class=\"skc-col-ours\"><span class=\"skc-check\">✓</span></td>\n              <td><span class=\"skc-cross\">✗</span></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>Hypoallergenic &amp; durable</td>\n              <td class=\"skc-col-ours\"><span class=\"skc-check\">✓</span></td>\n              <td><span class=\"skc-cross\">✗</span></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>Washable cover</td>\n              <td class=\"skc-col-ours\"><span class=\"skc-check\">✓</span></td>\n              <td><span class=\"skc-cross\">✗</span></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>Developed with experts</td>\n              <td class=\"skc-col-ours\"><span class=\"skc-check\">✓</span></td>\n              <td><span class=\"skc-cross\">✗</span></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>Try without risk</td>\n              <td class=\"skc-col-ours\"><span class=\"skc-check\">✓</span></td>\n              <td><span class=\"skc-cross\">✗</span></td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ===== 8. PHOTO STRIP ===== -->\n  <div class=\"skc-photo-strip\">\n    <img src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/snoozityyy.jpg\" alt=\"Product photo 1\" />\n    <img src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/gempages_576690581959344994-4fd19150-0016-49f3-b5ca-c4d78bf07a9f.webp\" alt=\"Product photo 2\" />\n    <img src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/gempages_576690581959344994-1fa79b1c-4e19-4fc1-9d5c-486508f1b829.jpg\" alt=\"Product photo 3\" />\n    <img src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/6_848b8939-8559-439a-bc61-b69f7c1acb57.webp\" alt=\"Product photo 4\" />\n    <img src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/gempages_576690581959344994-996dfc7e-acc1-4964-aa95-6ce185f6220d.webp\" alt=\"Product photo 5\" />\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ===== 9. EXPERT TESTIMONIALS ===== -->\n  <section class=\"skc-experts\">\n    <h2>Medically verified by independent experts in neck, back, and sleep health</h2>\n    <div class=\"skc-experts-grid\">\n\n      <div>\n        <img class=\"skc-expert-img\" src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/a-doctor-smiles-while-holding-her-clipboard.jpg\" alt=\"Expert Dr. Sarah Mitchell\" />\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-quote\">\"As a physician, I frequently see neck and back complaints that stem from poor sleep posture. This pillow provides the correct alignment and relief. I can confidently recommend it to anyone who wants to sleep better and wake up pain-free.\"</p>\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-name\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 14.5v-9l6 4.5-6 4.5z\"/></svg>\n          Dr. Sarah Mitchell\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-title\">Orthopedic Physician, specialized in neck &amp; back complaints</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <img class=\"skc-expert-img\" src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/New_version_2_1.png\" alt=\"Expert Dr. James Howell\" />\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-quote\">\"A good night's sleep starts with the right support. This pillow combines ergonomics with comfort, helping my patients finally experience less tension in their neck and shoulders. It's a valuable addition for anyone with sleep issues.\"</p>\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-name\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 14.5v-9l6 4.5-6 4.5z\"/></svg>\n          Dr. James Howell\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-title\">Physical Therapist &amp; sleep posture specialist</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <img class=\"skc-expert-img\" src=\"https://snoozity.nl/cdn/shop/files/445556.jpg\" alt=\"Expert Dr. Kevin Strauss\" />\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-quote\">\"Many people underestimate how important posture during sleep really is. This pillow helps bring the body into balance and supports the recovery process overnight. A smart choice for long-term health and wellbeing.\"</p>\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-name\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 14.5v-9l6 4.5-6 4.5z\"/></svg>\n          Dr. Kevin Strauss\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"skc-expert-title\">Health expert &amp; speaker on posture and recovery</p>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ===== 10. FAQ ===== -->\n  <section class=\"skc-faq\">\n    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"skc-faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"skc-faq-q\">Will this pillow help with my back, hip, or knee pain?</button>\n      <div class=\"skc-faq-a\">Poor sleep posture is a major cause of pain. Our support pillow helps reduce back, hip, and knee pain by supporting the natural alignment of your spine throughout the night. Side sleeping has never been safer or more comfortable!</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"skc-faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"skc-faq-q\">How quickly will this pillow help me?</button>\n      <div class=\"skc-faq-a\">Most customers notice a difference after the very first night. For full results, we recommend using the pillow for at least 7 to 14 nights so your body can adjust to the new ergonomic sleep position.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"skc-faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"skc-faq-q\">Is the pillow machine washable, and what is the pillowcase made of?</button>\n      <div class=\"skc-faq-a\">Yes, the pillowcase is fully machine washable at 86°F (30°C). The cover is made from a soft, breathable mesh fabric that feels comfortable against the skin and promotes moisture wicking for a fresher sleeping experience.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"skc-faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"skc-faq-q\">Will it improve my sleep?</button>\n      <div class=\"skc-faq-a\">Absolutely. By properly supporting your neck and spine, your body needs less effort to find a comfortable position. The result: less tossing and turning, deeper sleep, and waking up feeling far more refreshed.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"skc-faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"skc-faq-q\">How do you use the pillow?</button>\n      <div class=\"skc-faq-a\">Place the pillow so that the central recess cradles your head and the wings support your neck and shoulders. Whether you're a side sleeper or back sleeper, the pillow adapts to your body for optimal support throughout the night.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"skc-faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"skc-faq-q\">What payment methods do you accept?</button>\n      <div class=\"skc-faq-a\">We accept all major payment methods including credit card (Visa/Mastercard), PayPal, Klarna buy now pay later, and Apple Pay. All transactions are secured with SSL encryption.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"skc-faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"skc-faq-q\">Do you also sell this product on Amazon or another platform?</button>\n      <div class=\"skc-faq-a\">No, our pillow is exclusively available through our own webshop. This allows us to fully control the quality, pricing, and customer service — ensuring you always get the best possible experience.</div>\n    </div>\n\n  </section>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  document.querySelectorAll('.skc-faq-q').forEach(btn => {\n    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n      const item = btn.closest('.skc-faq-item');\n      const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');\n      document.querySelectorAll('.skc-faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));\n      if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');\n    });\n  });\n</script>\n"
      }
